ZH: 我从来不吃辣的食物。
EN: I never eat spicy food.

ZH: 她从来不迟到。
EN: She never arrives late.

ZH: 我从来不喜欢下雨天。
EN: I never like rainy days.

ZH: 他从来不说谎。
EN: He never tells lies.

ZH: 我从来没有去过澳大利亚。
EN: I have never been to Australia.

ZH: 我们从来没有见过这样大的海浪。
EN: We have never seen such big waves before.

ZH: 她从来没有想过会有这个机会。
EN: She never thought she would have this opportunity.

ZH: 我从来不吸烟。
EN: I never smoke.

ZH: 他们从来不吃肉。
EN: They never eat meat.

ZH: 我从来没有看过那部电影。
EN: I have never seen that movie.

ZH: 她从来不喜欢独自在家。
EN: She never likes to be alone at home.

ZH: 他从来没有见过如此美丽的风景。
EN: He has never seen such beautiful scenery.

ZH: 我们从来不想要有任何争吵。
EN: We never want to have any arguments.

ZH: 她从来不喜欢吃甜食。
EN: She never likes to eat sweets.

ZH: 我们从来没有试过那么难的挑战。
EN: We have never tried such a difficult challenge.

ZH: 他们从来都很害羞。
EN: They are always very shy.

ZH: 我们从来都很珍惜这段友谊。
EN: We always treasure this friendship.

ZH: 她从来都待人和善。
EN: She always treats people kindly.

ZH: 老师从来不允许迟到。
EN: The teacher never allows late arrivals.

ZH: 奶奶从来都照顾我们。
EN: Grandma always takes care of us.
